  "original_title": "\u0dbb\u0dcf\u0da2\u0db4\u0d9a\u0dca\u0dc2\u0dbd\u0dcf\u0d9c\u0dda \u0d9a\u0dd4\u0dab\u0dd4 \u0d85\u0daf\u0dd2\u0db1 \u0dbd\u0ddc\u0dbb\u0dd2 \u0db6\u0dc0\u0da7 \u0dc3\u0da2\u0db6 \u0d9a\u0dd2\u0dc3\u0dd2\u0dc0\u0d9a\u0dd4 \u0db4\u0dad\u0dca \u0dc0\u0db1\u0dca\u0db1\u0dd9 \u0db1\u0dd1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "No one will become Rajapaksa's garbage truck",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Mr. Sajith Premadasa, the opposition leader, said that it was the Rajapaksa regime that brought the country to such a precipice, and that no one in Samagi Janbalawega will become the Rajapaksa's garbage truck.",
        "The opposition leader said that today the whole country is facing an economic socio-political tragedy, and the reason for this is that the people took the wrong path instead of the right path in two elections in 2019 and 2020.",
        "He said this while attending the Constituency Committee meeting organized by Rakwana Samagi Janabalawega's organizer Mr. BK Ariyawansa.",
        "The leader of the opposition said that the latest miracle happening in the bankrupt country is the all-party government and what the country needs is not a country that wears ministerial gifts and goes behind the posts.",
        "Mr. Sajith Premadasa, the opposition leader, further said that there is no solution as an election should be held immediately and the people's decision should be sought."
      ],
